      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c4da78b7bed1cf4f623c97a"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Broaden your perspective, Victoria. Think beyond the Reach, beyond the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimwardPeriphery],Periphery]].\n\nOur Directorate is growing stronger, but we stand among giants. To the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSuccessorState],Successor States]], we are nothing—a tin-pot dictatorship in a galactic backwater, to be ignored or crushed as they please. If we are to survive in the long term, we need a strong ally… but we have nothing to offer in return.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
