    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cad8e28379c0c9f6a18a269"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "We cannot change our circumstances—the Reach is comparatively small and poor, and that is how it will remain.\n\nWhat we <i>can</i> do is shift the political balance of the Periphery. By engineering conflict, we can give ourselves value—as a buffer state and an ally of convenience.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": {
