      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cc3ff3333965c69f7503f19"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Yes. Your target is a port city that serves as the primary supplier of Perdition's aerospace bases. A chemical strike there will look like a back door attempt to undermine [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreThomasCalderon],Calderon]]'s military readiness. He'll assume that the method of attack was chosen for the purpose of plausible deniability.\n\nAnd when he points his finger at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHouseDavion],House Davion]] in response, I will quietly approach him with an offer of support.",
      "branches": [
