      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c5793bf944e41cc634b7651"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Then our Directorate will perish, and us alongside it. But inaction isn't an option, Victoria. An alliance built on a lie is better than no alliance at all, and our Directorate cannot survive indefinitely in a vacuum.\n\nI cannot trust a task this sensitive to any mercenary. It has to be someone who truly loves the Reach, and who <i>understands</i> the price of failure.",
