      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c4b557f3d25d986b8a38c85"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "I don't <i>enjoy</i> ordering you to do this. But I am trying to accomplish in five years what House Arano <i>should have</i> done across a span of three lifetimes. To safeguard the Reach on such a short timetable, risks must be taken—and sacrifices have to be made.\n\nShow me that you are the defender of the realm that I know you to be, and accept this terrible responsibility. Not for me, but for our people. For the Reach.",
