        "id": "9ca0f568b45a516585d529e9"
      },
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Gods. It doesn't even matter what else is in the archive—with this, we could turn the Taurians against the Directorate.\n\nProtector Calderon will want Espinosa's head on a plate.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "You're damn right he will. And I intend to sit back and watch the show.",
